{"tid":359439,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《想吃掉你的胰臟》不是恐怖片！上映2週被封淚崩神作","createTime":"2017-08-14T13:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T12:39:44.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d48a4713a40a7cab98dcb8524a8b906e74ef0be5","tid":359439,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"日本電影《我想吃掉你的胰臟》改編自同名漫畫，不少人看到片名以為是活屍吃人類的恐怖片，其實這是一部純愛系電影，在日上映2週就衝破日幣12億元（約台幣4億元）票房，不僅在日本主流電影網站「<a href=\"http://映画.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%98%A0%E7%94%BB.com&d=7fTgFZrTg15vyCwIFpNGxKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=ba83d3f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">映画.com</a>」獲得5分中的4.1高分，許多觀眾也紛紛表示，最後為了這句「我想吃掉你的胰臟」哭到不能自己。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2727/d2727912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2727%2Fd2727912.jpg&h=e1713613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼飾演男女主角的北村匠海、濱邊美波，自然生動演技廣受好評。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2727/d2727914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2727%2Fd2727914.jpg&h=271e3f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《我想吃掉你的胰臟》改編自熱門同名漫畫，片中描述「沒有名字的男主角」學生時代偶然間撿到一本「共病文庫」，得知同班女學生不久於人世，2個看似不可能有交集，卻從此意外變成彼此最依賴的人，「我想吃掉你的胰臟」原來不只是字面上的意義，不少觀眾都坦言最後為了這句台詞「哭到不能自己」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2727/d2727913.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2727%2Fd2727913.jpg&h=2ddb368d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼小栗旬和北川景子飾演長大後的男女主角。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2727/d2727924.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2727%2Fd2727924.jpg&h=1e930351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，《我》片在日上映2週，表現叫好又叫座，也獲得「漫畫小說改編最滿意電影」票選冠軍，許多觀眾都留言表示R8 Spyder V10善良猛獸，「第一次在電影院哭成這樣」、「超越想像的伏線令人動容」，也有人笑說：「隔壁座男子哭得太大聲，要再來重看一遍了。」被網友封為2017年採用Launch Control彈射系統起跑極其兇猛必看神片！"},{"pid":"26ad5613a923ed17ebdc767ad4eb48e866e32497","tid":359439,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"千雪呢??"},{"pid":"a89f32d2758d707778b946a7f8c200daf7af9bc5","tid":359439,"uid":46933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:29:43.000Z","msg":"關鍵字放得太後無意思<br />\n6分"},{"pid":"dbb30adb9eb432111ae524734d782fe3c464f2ee","tid":359439,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千雪呢??</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9ca33aca75d46163cbd8cc6eaa64ca75d0bc87ab","tid":359439,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"千雪BB呢"},{"pid":"45c6c7713836b0a3b011a8fc76ae3ae9066bc73b","tid":359439,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"女主唔太掂要扣分"},{"pid":"20203b0d2a2773c266d7778a183406800ca20aef","tid":359439,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個名係咪已經劇透左女主角個胰臟有病"},{"pid":"60b3a548acf24e29d6c7cc04d5365d202cc7b152","tid":359439,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"中二病片, 個女主角係咁同男主講自己有絕症就快死, 係咪痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b0388fbe5a3163853fd0a1547dacabcdd35ddb","tid":359439,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T04:11:04.000Z","msg":"重點係小栗旬同北川景子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41be851e911947d8afd992cdc5a3583fdf987466","tid":359439,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T12:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重點係小栗旬同北川景子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}